body:
&quot;She makes her way to the plaza&rsquo;s northern archway as a massively bearded man with metaled shoulder guards and an iron skullcap enters. His arms are pneumatic, piston-driven monstrosities, and Tamara recognizes one of the nameless hierophant cultists of the Glorious Evolved.&quot;

This is what it said while I was reading the Progress Day storyline. I took a look at his picture. The details seem pretty close.

But I wonder what he's doing there if that was really him. Maybe snatch up some advanced tech or gather some thugs to join his conquest in taking back Bilgewater, with a new Battleship with more advanced tech than his last one.
